2009-04-15  Adrien DELLE CAVE <decryptus@proformatique.com>

	pf_magic_pickupmark
	$Revision$
	$Date$

	Added possibility to do a magic pickup with PICKUPMARK.
	PICKUPMARK variable can contains multiple extensions separated by an '&'.

